channel.title: Go Gecko Go and more - by Cheddr [beats, synthwave, remix, playlist]
channel.description:
These older tracks are probably as complete as they are going to get. DM me know if you'd like to remix any of these and I'll send you the file or stems. I think there are some good ideas in here but I don't plan on working on these any more. I think remixes of any of these would be really interesting.
_Playlist:_ https://soundcloud.com/cheddr/sets/misc-auxy-v4-beats-and
